name: Fallen °_°
description:
Once they were fierce and brave
now they are gone,
lost in the battlefield
their bodies cold and stiff
never to return home

Their families left behind
grieving for their loved ones
who died in battle
will never be forgotten

Their courage and bravery
will be remembered forever
and they will always be
warriors fallen in the battlefield.
